{"tid":1013042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無心插柳柳成蔭？爆乳正妹拍AV 竟假戲真做成真愛","createTime":"2019-02-08T05:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T14:03:42.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0e678b95417d92bc637cf0e2ed36c167bf344d","tid":1013042,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/07/99/5897228.jpg&amp;s=Y&amp;x=17&amp;y=0&amp;sw=548&amp;sh=365&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F99%2F5897228.jpg%26s%3DY%26x%3D17%26y%3D0%26sw%3D548%26sh%3D365%26exp%3D3600&h=33efdff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年僅20歲的德國AV女優名叫涅絲比特，擁有傲人的火辣身材。 圖／翻攝自每日星報<br />\n一名20歲AV女優和大她36歲的AV男優，3年前合作拍一部情色片，戲中兩人「啪啪啪」享受著床上高潮境界，想不到就此認定彼此是「對的人」，私下交往一斷時間後，已計畫要共同走入婚姻。<br />\n這名年僅20歲的德國AV女優名叫涅絲比特（Lou Nesbit），未婚夫則是56歲的AV男優科瓦斯基（Egon Kowalski）。儘管兩人認定彼此是基於真愛才交往，然而外界卻不看好這對「父女戀」，甚至有AV片的觀眾質疑涅絲比特是為了錢才看上科瓦斯基，對他倆極盡冷嘲熱諷。<br />\n對此，涅絲比特表示，雖然以科瓦斯基的年齡，足以成為她的父親，但她與科瓦斯基卻是真心相愛，絕非為了錢或性。涅絲比特還大讚科瓦斯基是個富有幽默感的熟男，凡事都能了解對方想法。她說：「真愛是不管年齡、外表和性別的，只要在一起能快樂和滿足，就是真愛。」不管外界怎麼評斷他們這對情侶，至少彼此雙方的家族都能接受這段「父女戀」，才會有結婚的打算。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/07/99/5897230.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F99%2F5897230.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=de153492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/07/99/5897231.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F99%2F5897231.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=118b235a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n20歲的AV女優涅絲比特與56歲的AV男優科瓦斯基假戲真做，把做愛化為真愛，兩人已計畫走入婚姻。 圖／翻攝自每日星報<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3633409?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F3633409%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1MeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=7e82221d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3633409?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"372562fbae45e2fa1273b61eec041a11e563d6dc","tid":1013042,"uid":212399,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472467991bfee8ef58d11cee0391270982d25cb1","tid":1013042,"uid":150857,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"似50歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab6ce316ff910bafcb5fd53b75e15e3a7734588","tid":1013042,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c325c1489b91fab91d84c13ab0c4efa8713754","tid":1013042,"uid":66974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"男一開頭睇錯36，佢明顯5,60啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後面睇到56, 合理。女就40歲樣，佢唔係皮膚好就50歲"},{"pid":"4b58ab9cb2fae1533e289e8cb707f80ac06b83b5","tid":1013042,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919237d45bdbac80b2d405a69fb020199adad241","tid":1013042,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:55:46.000Z"